    "title": "Rāg Darabāri kānaḍā",
    "section": "Lyrics",
    "text": "Lyrics\n\nSthāyī\n\nacala birāja ho siṃhāsana baiṭhe\nrājādhirāja rājārāma pṛthvī para\n\nAntarā\n\ntakhata bakhata tumhi dino karatāra\nnistāra karana ko, ānanda bhayo taha pura ghara ghara\n\nSanchārī\n\naneka aneka bhātanako naga naga takhata śobhā deta\nmāno indu jyota jhala mala kara\n\nĀbhog\n\ntānasena tua guṇa kaha na sakata\nastuta karata saba loga aura tuhi jahāna para-eka nara"
  },
