  {
    "objectID": "chapters/aju_bahata_sugandha.html#lyrics",
    "href": "chapters/aju_bahata_sugandha.html#lyrics",
    "title": "Rāg Bahār",
    "section": "Lyrics",
    "text": "Lyrics\n\nSthāyī\n\nāju bahata sugandha pavana sumanda madhura basanta me\nhara makura para yutha madhupa madahara nirata kara rava kuñja me\n\nAntarā\n\nkahi koyaliyā kuhu karahi āmuvā ke ḍāra raṅga me\nkahi beli cāmeli gulāba gendā campa raṅga biraṅga me\n\nSanchārī\n\nita jobana madamātī yuvati jvali rahī bina kāntame\npūkāra ghana hā nātha nātha vihata bhai prāṇāntame\n\nĀbhog\n\nsuni śravaṇa rava raṅganātha kahata bacāve nātha kusaṅga me\nehi raṅga ḍhaṅga anaṅga mada so utārī rākha susaṅga me\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nNoteReading the notation\n\n\n\n\n\nTīvrā tāl is a 7-beat cycle divided as 3 + 2 + 2. Each row below shows two consecutive cycles side-by-side: the first seven columns form one cycle (sam X at beat 1, vibhāgs 2 and 3 marking beats 4 and 6), and the next seven columns form the following cycle."
  },
